      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented verification test suite and version-controlled release process consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with FDA-validated solver release. Version control, regression testing, and change logs documented. SQA level 2 achieved."
