      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal use error analysis is not required; documented analyst qualifications and peer review of simulation setup are sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by independent CFD engineer with 8 years rotating machinery experience. Boundary condition specification and turbulence model selection documented and peer-reviewed. Formal use error quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
