      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, statistical characterization of experimental sample variability is not required; use of published mean experimental values is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis data from FDA interlaboratory study (Herbertson et al. 2015) used as validation reference. Mean values across laboratories used; sample-level statistical characterization not required at MRL 2."
