    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Output comparison achieves gradation 3, exceeding the MRL 2 requirement of gradation 2. GCI of 2.8% confirms adequate discretization. Predicted NIH values within 15% of FDA benchmark experimental data across all operating points. RH < 1 acceptance criterion met for worst-case operating condition (3500 RPM, 2 L/min). Assessment team concludes simulation evidence is credible for the stated COU and recommends acceptance for regulatory submission.",
